  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to see if children and adolescents with poorly controlled type 1
      diabetes will benefit from using a continuous glucose monitor (CGM), a device that can be
      used to check blood sugars.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
